  </p>
  <p id='active_teams_count'>&nbsp;</p>
  <p>
    <small>
      built by <a href="https://crazyoptimist.net" target="_blank">crazyoptimist</a>&nbsp; on top of <a href="https://github.com/slack-ruby/slack-ruby-bot-server" target="_blank">slack-ruby-bot</a>, <a href="https://github.com/CrazyOptimist/slack-rails-bot-starter" target="_blank">fork me on github</a>
    </small>
  </p>
 </body>
</html>

